<p>She picks up her controller. The round starts.</p>
<p>She focuses on the game. She is not focusing on the game at all. His hand is very warm. At some point his thumb moves — just barely, against the fabric — a slow, barely-there pressure. She misses three shots she would normally land in her sleep.</p>
